{
  "stem": "142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] When they took us out of the camp to go to the quarantine on this [? place, ?] they would-- would put the number with a pen, with a pen that wrote-- actually was putting down [INAUDIBLE] writing the numbers.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then afterward they finish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At the end, I had a-- I know was swollen for 20 days before it came back to normal.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "182568.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not before, but after, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "During the quarantine, you got the number.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was full of my family, [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mores ?] Venezia family-- and [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mores, ?] Venezia, and Shlomo, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "These are the three that I remember being with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were in the same one, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I knew them, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That there was a long process, was very, very good when you have people who around you, you know, because you don't know where you're going.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We [INAUDIBLE] know that we will be killed right away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that was very good news when you had people around you looking at each other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By talking.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing I can remember is, you know, don't stop talking.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even if you don't know anything, you try to have a conversation of any kind to be able to forget what the-- the balance of your voyage will be.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, no, the situation was very, very intense, when-- to find out-- because everybody was thinking what [INAUDIBLE] are going to be happening, because we didn't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Once we don't know what our faith will be, always you make assumptions of kinds, that we'll be OK, we will not be OK.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are going to do this, we are going to do that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But nobody knew that we are going to die.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
